                "text": "Yes, Detective. Anything to solve my sister's case",
                "expression": "neutral"
            },
            {
                "character": "Elias",
                "text": "I need to see the guest list of the party yesterday. One of the servants told me Lady Eleanor talked to three people during the party. And I suppose you are the one with the black mask, correct?",
