            },
            {
                "character": "Blackwood",
                "text": "Yes indeed, Detective. I was the one wearing the black mask during the party. And for the guest list... Mr. Henshaw was the one who was in charge of the party, he's the only person who has the list.",
                "expression": "neutral"
            },
            {
                "character": "Elias",
                "text": "Okay, I shall go look for him now. Thank you for you cooperation, My Lord.",
                "expression": "neutral"
            },
            {
                "character": "Blackwood",
                "text": "Why, of course. It is of utmost importance we find the scum who did this to my sister",
                "expression": "neutral"
            },
            {
                "character": "Elias",
                "text": "(I have to go search for Mr. Henshaw now)",
                "expression": "neutral"
            },
